                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for preparing 2, 3-butanediol through dehydrogenation coupling of photochemical oxidation ethanol",
                    "一种光化学氧化乙醇脱氢偶联制备2,3-丁二醇的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for preparing 2, 3-butanediol through dehydrogenation coupling of photochemical oxidation ethanol, and belongs to the technical field of photochemical synthesis. In an ethanol and solvent reaction system, under an inert atmosphere, hydrogen peroxide is used as an oxidant, and illumination ethanol dehydrogenation coupling is carried out to synthesize 2, 3-butanediol. Under the driving of light, the hydrogen peroxide solution is decomposed to generate hydroxyl free radicals, the hydroxyl free radicals have strong oxidizability, ethanol can be oxidized to remove a next hydrogen proton at an alpha position to generate hydroxyethyl free radicals, and the hydroxyethyl free radicals are subjected to carbon-carbon coupling to generate 2, 3-butanediol. The addition of Fe < 2 + > and oxide can catalyze decomposition of hydrogen peroxide to form hydroxyl radicals, so that the reaction efficiency is improved. The method is simple in process, environment-friendly, free of secondary pollution and low in cost, and the product is easy to separate and high in selectivity which can reach 85% or above."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种光化学氧化乙醇脱氢偶联制备2,3‑丁二醇的方法，属于光化学合成技术领域。本发明在乙醇与溶剂反应体系中，惰性气氛下，利用过氧化氢作为氧化剂，光照乙醇脱氢偶联合成2,3‑丁二醇。过氧化氢溶液在光的驱动下，发生分解产生羟基自由基，其具有强的氧化性，可将乙醇氧化在α位脱下一个氢质子，生成羟乙基自由基，羟乙基自由基碳碳偶联生成2,3‑丁二醇。Fe2+及氧化物的加入可以催化过氧化氢分解形成羟基自由基，从而提高反应效率。本发明工艺简单、环境友好，无二次污染、成本低廉、而且产物易分离，选择性高，可达到85％以上。"
                }
            ]
